---
// about us section
---


<section class="bg-[#fff0e0] py-16 border-b-1 border-cyan-600">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-5 items-center">

      <!-- Right: Content -->
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 space-y-6">
        <h1 class="text-4xl text-right font-bold">Make your Gift as Unique as Emontions</h1>

        <p class="text-main text-3xl leading-relaxed text-right">
          Add your favorite items, choose wrapping styles, and write heartfelt messages - all in one place. Make every celebration unforgettable with gifts that truly speak from your heart.
        </p>          

        <p class="text-main text-3xl leading-relaxed text-right">
          At Gifterra we believe that a great gift to more than just on them it's
          on experience. We specialize in curating and customizing beautiful gift
          packs filled with high-quality, thoughtful products. Our mission is to
          make gifting a joyful and seamless experience for everyone.
        </p>

      </div>

      <!-- Left: Image -->
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-start-8 md:col-span-5 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-blue-100">
        <img
          src="/images/other-images/about.jpg"
          alt="About us"
          class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  
</section>
